com.adobe.fd.signatures.client.types.exceptions

Interface ExceptionMsgIds

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CredentialLoginException, DocTimeStampNotApplicable, DuplicateSignatureFieldException, FIPSComplianceException, InvalidArgumentException, MissingSignatureFieldException, NoCertifyingSignatureException, PDFOperationException, PermissionsException, SeedValueValidationException, SignatureFieldNotSignedException, SignatureFieldSignedException, SignaturesBaseException, SignaturesBaseRuntimeException, SignaturesOtherException, SignatureVerifyException, SigningException

    public interface ExceptionMsgIds
    Maps Exception message names to their identification codes. These codes are used to read actual message string from a localized file.
